  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-14732">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 1. </span>
      Select three of the professions from Group 1 listed below which interest
      you, then complete the following:<br /><br /><strong>Group 1:</strong
      ><br />
      (1) Allopathic physician (MD)—all specialties<br />
      (2) Osteopathic physician (DO)—all specialties<br />
      (3) Podiatrist (DPM)<br />
      (4) Chiropractor (DC)<br />
      (5) Nurse Practitioner (NP)<br />(6) Psychologist (PhD or PsyD)<br />(7)
      Optometrist (OD)<br />(8) Audiologist (AudD)
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-14732 mb-requirement-id-14733">
        (a) Briefly describe to your counselor the roles these professionals
        play in the delivery of health care.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-14732 mb-requirement-id-14734">
        (b) Describe to your counselor the educational and licensing
        requirements for the professionals you selected.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
